Comparable.documentation: Ancestor of types with total order relation defined, i.e. '<' and '='.
Comparable.name: Comparable

Date.documentation: Date type based on IS8601 representation.
Date.name: Date

Time.documentation: Time type based on IS8601 representation.
Time.name: Time

Date_time.documentation: Date Time type based on IS8601 representation.
Date_time.name: Date_time

Duration.documentation: Duration type based on IS8601 representation.
Duration.name: Duration

Interval.documentation: Type defining an interval of any ordered type.
Interval.name: Interval

Hash.documentation: Type defining Hash table / hash map structure, whose type parameters V and K represent a value type and an Comparable key type respectively.
Hash.name: Hash
